<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.190756>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 6. Acizzia veski, sp. nov. (1), Head, male, (dorsal aspect, from slide); (2), habitus, male, (dorsal aspect); (3), habitus, female, (dorsal aspect); (4), habitus, male (lateral aspect); (5), habitus, female (lateral aspect); (6), forewing, male. Scale = 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/190756/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.190757>
    dc:description "FIGURES 7 – 10. Acizzia veski, sp. nov. (7), Male terminalia (lateral aspect); (8), paramere (inner face, lateral aspect); (9), female terminalia, (lateral aspect); (10), fifth (final) instar nymph (ventral aspect, left; dorsal aspect right). Scale = 0.2 mm in Figs 7 – 9, 0.5 mm in Fig. 10." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/190757/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

